Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在被星光照射的顶屋里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.90,0:00:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,独自一人聆听着天空的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.55,0:00:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用玻璃的绷带遮住眼睛行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是孤独的马戏团孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.85,0:00:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孤身一人的悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,震动的绷带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.87,0:00:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撼动着心灵……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.35,0:01:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用温柔的眼神期待与某人的相会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.05,0:01:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳边细语“请留在我身边”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.27,0:01:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silent Voice

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.39,0:01:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救起奇怪的货船后\N我们又救起拉莎拉和莎拉莎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.73,0:01:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意外地,货船上竟然隐藏了MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.39,0:01:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于莫迪的活耀表现\N我们才击退敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.53,0:01:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回想起来\N月月的两位小姐好像成了我和哈曼之间的防护罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.24,0:01:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我乃不知道哈曼在我附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.07,0:02:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四十话\N老虎巴姆之梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.98,0:02:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他们这么讨厌我们?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.58,0:02:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右边,往右边避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.25,0:02:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇斯\N他说右边啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.00,0:02:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你闭嘴,静静看着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.74,0:02:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经发出讯号了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.38,0:02:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个,那个 \N你吵死了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.55,0:02:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,来不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.26,0:02:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放下防御幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.44,0:02:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会...会被击中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.95,0:02:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻击鱼雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.17,0:02:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.18,0:03:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后一个吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.37,0:03:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是中立空域吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.67,0:03:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为战争时\N有那么简单中立吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.80,0:03:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.61,0:03:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好豪华的殖民地啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.59,0:03:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是以旧世纪的香港为模仿对象的殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.63,0:03:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.26,0:03:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打开通讯回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.64,0:03:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打开舰桥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.51,0:03:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不知道考虑巴姆的入境条件吗!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,入境条件?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.32,0:03:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我代替史丹巴总监警告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.04,0:03:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新亚加玛的船员和\N平名在内都一定要下船...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.21,0:03:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么?\N走开!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.00,0:04:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MS也不准动用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.40,0:04:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禁止开炮\N别开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.06,0:04:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才若不开炮\N我们的舰桥就被鱼雷击破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.34,0:04:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走开!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.50,0:04:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N干什么连这里也要贴?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.65,0:04:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以上是入境条件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.47,0:04:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么严吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.09,0:04:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贴上的封条是绝对不准撕下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.17,0:04:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈曼大人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.70,0:04:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别在意,这是了解\N一般市民作风的好机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.74,0:04:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,检查完后立刻下船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.08,0:04:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高达吗?这个值钱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.88,0:04:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新亚加玛...\N-被绳子给绑着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.99,0:04:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你们停留期间与人开战\N那我们就无珐中立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.78,0:04:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会做那种事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.80,0:05:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着,我们总监史丹巴大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.86,0:05:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直致力于让殖民地\N成为永远没有战火的殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.93,0:05:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史丹普?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.05,0:05:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是史丹巴大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.40,0:05:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们老虎巴姆殖民地\N被治理成一大观光地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.49,0:05:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这都归功于\N史丹巴阁下英明领导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.69,0:05:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来他是游乐园的园长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.50,0:05:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.54,0:05:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,游乐园不是和平的象征吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.16,0:05:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.47,0:05:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里?\N进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.95,0:05:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是中立殖民地\N也应该说清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.24,0:05:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才全都说清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太霸道了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.96,0:05:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.52,0:05:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那边,你们到那边!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.58,0:05:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早有听闻\N想不到竟是这么有风格的殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.03,0:05:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.75,0:06:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才想上巴士的是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.87,0:06:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.15,0:06:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是船员,抓到也没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.69,0:06:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是要跟高达交换吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.48,0:06:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要抓对人才有用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.31,0:06:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这女人\N看起来似乎很倔强,很有劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.68,0:06:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带这女人来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.99,0:06:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢带来有冲劲的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.84,0:06:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.03,0:06:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么,普通的装饰品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.27,0:06:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你快搭上那班巴士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.17,0:06:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是右边的巴士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.18,0:06:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?看不见啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.58,0:06:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你搭左边的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.98,0:06:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.50,0:06:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可口的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.37,0:06:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.88,0:06:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差点被看出监视摄影机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.50,0:06:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.00,0:06:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要把人分开?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.60,0:06:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该能自由行动吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.97,0:06:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.67,0:07:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位,他们能接纳我们\N我们就该存感谢之心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.07,0:07:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你们的做法也有可议之处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.06,0:07:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实你只要说出理由\N我们就会遵从的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.72,0:07:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是和平的殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.95,0:07:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须对军人加以监视\N
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.13,0:07:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要分类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.92,0:07:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了,我们确实有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉莎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.98,0:07:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们...\N又发现好女人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.98,0:07:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该还有更美的,再找找吧\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.78,0:07:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎办?露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.45,0:07:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉莎说的对,艾莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.71,0:07:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,把他们都带过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.61,0:07:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.29,0:07:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把男人给我分开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.46,0:07:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.80,0:07:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个殖民地的长官叫史丹巴吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.41,0:07:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.51,0:07:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的品味不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.09,0:07:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.04,0:07:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是亚加玛救起的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.58,0:08:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也被派上这辆车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.58,0:08:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这殖民地很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.29,0:08:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.80,0:08:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许这是光之神的决定吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.65,0:08:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.69,0:08:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.61,0:08:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样任人摆布好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.50,0:08:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只能暂时观望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉他们不知要不要紧呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.49,0:08:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.96,0:08:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们到专用宿舍去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.72,0:08:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.87,0:08:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.45,0:08:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.67,0:08:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.26,0:08:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勉强还可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.34,0:08:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小子,你们想干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.55,0:08:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全体下车,乖乖听从指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.35,0:08:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.98,0:08:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.62,0:08:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么一回事??
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.77,0:08:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要捉你们当人质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到外面来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.33,0:08:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人质?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.37,0:08:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔,你快想办法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.27,0:09:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他昏的真是合时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.60,0:09:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想反抗吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.98,0:09:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你这么做!\N我会照办吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.73,0:09:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.80,0:09:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.62,0:09:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖把高达交出来\N什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.40,0:09:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开\N乖一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.44,0:09:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.43,0:09:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.68,0:09:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.13,0:09:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站着!可恶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.73,0:09:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小子,我不会让你轻易逃走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.16,0:09:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放...放开我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.67,0:09:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想偷高达?\N放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.85,0:09:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是史丹巴要求的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.80,0:09:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.73,0:09:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个也抓住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.46,0:09:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是想要MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.72,0:09:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是史丹巴的手下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.92,0:09:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要MS做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.84,0:09:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然是拿去卖钱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.54,0:09:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卖?\N不然我们付不出税金的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.43,0:10:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,税金?原来是为了付税金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.62,0:10:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.97,0:10:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是小孩子\N不付税金就会被送去矿山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.50,0:10:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的殖民地就是这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.04,0:10:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他女人被送上别的巴士对吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.24,0:10:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史丹巴喜欢挑选美女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.66,0:10:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送到他的后宫去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.80,0:10:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.99,0:10:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个后宫在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说详细点\N是真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.63,0:10:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说就是了\N你放了我才能说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.05,0:10:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很破旧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.10,0:10:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.61,0:10:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.24,0:10:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是欢迎的客人\N快来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙拉莎\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.72,0:10:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收藏那种MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.64,0:11:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史丹巴到底有什么阴谋?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.60,0:11:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰治他们没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.01,0:11:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.24,0:11:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有阿尔宾他们带路\N已经去地下旅馆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.22,0:11:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留在这里不是比较好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.44,0:11:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,回去新亚加玛最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.49,0:11:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对,只有我们的话\N当作全体被绑架就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.02,0:11:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个很美啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.38,0:11:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先声明\N我们不是受你们指使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.47,0:11:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是想给史丹巴看看颜色\N才协助你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.61,0:11:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洋装?\N我讨厌这打扮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.04,0:11:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉沙拉有危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.60,0:11:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样打扮很漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.95,0:11:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别用奇怪眼光看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.95,0:11:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再慢吞吞啊\N我们的船可能被辛吉翁发现而发展成战争的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.93,0:11:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁南...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.75,0:11:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎会呢?\N可是我们甚至连逃出这里的钱都没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.76,0:11:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要\N从史丹巴的口袋挖钱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.18,0:11:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N鲁南!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.09,0:12:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,我们也走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.78,0:12:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我们来这种地方干什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.90,0:12:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到亚加玛船上\N有这么多美女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.99,0:12:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这表示说 \N我也能以我的魅力控制亚加玛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.76,0:12:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们能住在这舒适地方\N或许是光的引导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.36,0:12:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊是想拯救你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.88,0:12:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的好意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.02,0:12:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问你想怎样救我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.56,0:12:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的心理隐藏着秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.89,0:12:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让那秘密暴露在阳光下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.39,0:12:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用你管\N请别再说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.93,0:12:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一再欺骗自己\N是永远见不到阳光的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.67,0:13:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想与这些奇怪的人\N住在同一房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.03,0:13:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再给我一间房间吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.27,0:13:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.60,0:13:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照她的话做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.37,0:13:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.68,0:13:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.29,0:13:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那女人保留到最后\N先要最鲜嫩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.47,0:13:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸妈妈死掉后我们无家可归\N姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.94,0:13:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.38,0:13:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们姐妹不太像啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.66,0:13:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以拜托叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.31,0:13:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们在史丹巴大人这里工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.75,0:13:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还太小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.21,0:13:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都肯做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.49,0:13:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且最年长的,长的不够可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好过份,太过份了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.29,0:13:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别伤心,长的粗壮也有工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.81,0:13:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带她们进去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.52,0:13:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.53,0:13:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也进去\N这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.22,0:14:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,那边也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.07,0:14:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个能用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.49,0:14:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.78,0:14:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MS真不少啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.81,0:14:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.97,0:14:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史丹巴大人很快会驾临的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.84,0:14:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.88,0:14:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不先请我们喝杯茶,好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.50,0:14:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们获邀到大人的后宫\N还啰唆这么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.99,0:14:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.40,0:14:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎到我的城堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.91,0:14:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的小姐\N都会受到我诚心招待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.06,0:14:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.10,0:14:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必要时就动手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.81,0:14:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里交给姊姊处理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.96,0:14:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是衷心欢迎你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.87,0:14:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,你的心是封闭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.29,0:14:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.92,0:15:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,健康的心才能看到光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.49,0:15:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充满欲望与恶意的心\N是看不到光明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.89,0:15:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有\N给予那种人帮忙也是一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.41,0:15:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来\N所以请打开你的心看清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.86,0:15:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会看清楚的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.00,0:15:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人,你没事吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会敲门的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.62,0:15:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你站在门口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.81,0:15:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.35,0:15:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实是这样的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.98,0:15:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么丑女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.08,0:15:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们自愿来后宫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没父没母无家可归
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.60,0:15:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...捷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.27,0:15:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉莎,我们到那边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.11,0:15:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没征询我允许\N就放这些人进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.50,0:15:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.75,0:15:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的\N这女孩跟那个留下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.95,0:15:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个丑女给我赶出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.56,0:15:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.61,0:15:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么...\N这声音也很难听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.26,0:16:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的人走掉了\N我们继续吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.68,0:16:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么打扮成这样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.88,0:16:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很适合吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.47,0:16:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别哭了,被赶走比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.86,0:16:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道留下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.31,0:16:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会被强迫做什么事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.61,0:16:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别那么沮丧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要怪我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.40,0:16:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家等着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.39,0:16:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的女孩子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.69,0:16:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.83,0:16:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.39,0:16:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.59,0:16:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.14,0:16:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,锁匙吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.10,0:16:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不许动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.63,0:16:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.10,0:16:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.49,0:16:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点\N知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.08,0:17:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.93,0:17:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.66,0:17:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在干什么?\N鲁南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.76,0:17:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会一直看你们脸色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.16,0:17:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有枪声,你们没听见吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.43,0:17:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外观很老旧\N可是驾驶舱是新的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.42,0:17:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是收藏品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.33,0:17:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小艇,小艇,快准备小艇\N知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.64,0:17:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老虎巴姆的象征\N需要你们这么美的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.68,0:17:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是伊莱说的事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.67,0:17:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.65,0:17:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚...什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.90,0:17:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的MS阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁在开动?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.17,0:17:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这感觉...是捷度.桑捷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.48,0:17:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛...这MS的操纵真难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.15,0:17:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.95,0:18:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是暴动,干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.05,0:18:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史...史丹巴大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.60,0:18:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.80,0:18:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉,在哪里?露卡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.76,0:18:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,在这里啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.74,0:18:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个窗户
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.96,0:18:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.87,0:18:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你退后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.59,0:18:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.14,0:18:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动作快点啊\N这地方是经不起袭击的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.00,0:18:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做的好啊,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.63,0:18:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人数目很多啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.82,0:18:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要碍我的事!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.04,0:18:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么MS?这个虐待狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.82,0:18:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.41,0:19:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的动作怎么会这么快的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.45,0:19:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你知道外表不等于实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.69,0:19:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我,鲁南!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.75,0:19:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是比查吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.13,0:19:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史丹巴在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.54,0:19:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要抓住他,勒索一笔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.39,0:19:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,后面啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.89,0:19:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很强啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.61,0:19:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.88,0:19:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁南...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.21,0:19:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.11,0:19:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁南,快逃\N实力相差太远了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.05,0:19:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想和我打吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.71,0:19:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度.桑捷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.68,0:19:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这声音...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.59,0:20:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哈曼吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.10,0:20:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又见面了,捷度.桑捷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.34,0:20:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.82,0:20:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想再和你谈一次话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.35,0:20:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才来见你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.63,0:20:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听从我的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.53,0:20:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样我便承认你是新人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.03,0:20:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你免于白死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.67,0:20:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会白死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.73,0:20:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还不知道吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当然知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.20,0:20:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们大人掀起的战争\N总是拖累所有人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.80,0:20:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说话太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.05,0:20:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不喜欢\n去讨大人的欢心啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.17,0:20:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.23,0:20:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错,你不敢杀人\N你是可爱的小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.31,0:21:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.26,0:21:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.23,0:21:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么哈曼会来这里的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.31,0:21:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差点便成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.18,0:21:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史丹巴那些愚蠢东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.75,0:21:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船员被绑架\N你们的警备令我无法放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.07,0:21:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是入境条件...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.11,0:21:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.73,0:21:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会外出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.45,0:21:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请让我做启航准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.76,0:21:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.26,0:21:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁南,没问题吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.12,0:21:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.49,0:21:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会救我们的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.58,0:21:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们让我学到很多东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.32,0:21:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.72,0:21:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是史丹巴的霸道\N使得老虎巴姆卷入战火的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.59,0:21:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,请小心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.87,0:21:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个殖民地已经被恶念袭卷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.80,0:21:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.86,0:21:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个恶念急速扩大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.71,0:21:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因为哈曼吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.70,0:22:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对,应该是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.34,0:22:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.21,0:22:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前哈曼的恶意\N怎么没伤到捷度他们的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.39,0:22:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是由于我们的保护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.58,0:22:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.53,0:22:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人的邪恶重叠过多时\N清高美丽的花朵很有可能被压溃的...

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.30,0:22:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成百 成万 上亿的繁星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.49,0:22:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何只是闪耀而已 展示你言语的能力吧 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.55,0:23:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我也能不回头地 让心灵出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.70,0:23:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若能把多如繁星的生命储存的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.65,0:23:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把整个银河也化作光芒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.35,0:23:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化作紧握在掌心的 生命的重量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.32,0:23:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我仍未能看见宇宙的路标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.22,0:23:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手掌触摸着一千万年的光芒

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.39,0:23:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈曼预料到了我们试图离开史丹巴的殖民卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.76,0:23:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果出不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.81,0:23:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其后 史丹巴驾驶MS攻过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.91,0:23:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这小孩一般的……不对  嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.14,0:24:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒙德 别太冒险了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.70,0:24:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一个敌人要出来了！不能哭着作战啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.89,0:24:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 高达ZZ 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.73,0:24:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉莎拉的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.37,0:24:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉莎 你真是冷静呢
